{"parentUuid":"246e2ea7-dda5-4bc3-b558-47ec930ff06c","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_0163nLGYxbkGzLxbdkUjhp92","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ran the actual numbers (required upscale factor per source vs. every generated tier) rather than going from memory:\n\n**Genuinely need a bigger source (upscale on the big banner tier, and two of them even bleed into the 1200px thumb tier):**\n\n| Post | Image | Native size | Thumb 1200w | Banner 2000w |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| The geometry of software teams | `geometry.jpg` | 1440×1121 | upscales (1.24×) | upscales (1.39×) |\n| Taking Charge of Your Career Growth | `growth.jpg` | 1558×1116 | upscales (1.24×) | upscales (1.28×) |\n| Increase your hiring success with job success profiles | `handshake.jpg` (currently `interview.jpg`) | 1403×1346 | upscales (1.03×, barely) | upscales (1.43×) |\n\n**Fine at the thumb tier, but marginal on the banner's biggest tier:**\n\n| Post | Image | Native size | Banner 2000w |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Estimating your way to success | `writing.jpg` | 1687×2519 | upscales (1.19×) |\n\n**Plenty of headroom everywhere (no replacement needed):** `filter.jpg` (2272×1408), `hypothesis.jpg` (2456×2226).\n\nIf you're hunting for replacements, `geometry.jpg` and `handshake`/`interview.jpg` are the two worth prioritizing — they're short on both dimensions relative to what a full-bleed banner needs. As a rule of thumb, anything **at least ~2000px on the shorter side** clears every tier we generate (thumb + banner) with margin."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":131,"cache_creation_input_tokens":747,"cache_read_input_tokens":178631,"output_tokens":567,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":747,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_t